GSD.description:
io-wq: Fix memory leak in worker creation

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.0.4 by commit ed981911a7c90a604f4a2bee908ab07e3b786aca, it was introduced in version v5.14 by commit 0e03496d1967abf1ebb151a24318c07d07f41f7f. For more details please see the references link.
